{"title":"MD 文件的基本语法","slug":"MD文件的基本语法","date":"2024-01-19","updated":"2024-01-20","comments":true,"path":"api/posts/26104.json","excerpt":null,"cover":"/gallery/A1.png","covers":["/gallery/A1.png"],"content":"<p>Hello！这篇文章起源于 <a href=\"//gist.github.com/apackeer/4159268\">这里</a> 是为了给大家演示下超酷的 MD 文件！</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这篇文章几乎包含了所有 Markdown 的魔法！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"开头\"><a href=\"# 开头\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"开头~\"></a>开头~</h1><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\"># H1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">## H2</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">### H3</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">#### H4</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">##### H5</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">###### H6</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">Alt-H1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">======</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">Alt-H2</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">------</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"H1\"><a href=\"#H1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"H1\"></a>H1</h1><h2 id=\"H2\"><a href=\"#H2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"H2\"></a>H2</h2><h3 id=\"H3\"><a href=\"#H3\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"H3\"></a>H3</h3><h4 id=\"H4\"><a href=\"#H4\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"H4\"></a>H4</h4><h5 id=\"H5\"><a href=\"#H5\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"H5\"></a>H5</h5><h6 id=\"H6\"><a href=\"#H6\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"H6\"></a>H6</h6><p>还可以用下划线来表示 H1 和 H2 噢！：</p>\n<h1 id=\"Alt-H1\"><a href=\"#Alt-H1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Alt-H1\"></a>Alt-H1</h1><h2 id=\"Alt-H2\"><a href=\"#Alt-H2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Alt-H2\"></a>Alt-H2</h2><h2 id=\"强调字体\"><a href=\"# 强调字体\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"强调字体~\"></a>强调字体~</h2><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">斜体魔法：<span class=\"emphasis\">* 斜体 *</span>、<span class=\"emphasis\">_斜体_</span>。</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">粗体魔法： <span class=\"strong\">** 粗体 **</span> or <span class=\"strong\">__粗体__</span>.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">曦煦阁的秘密组合： <span class=\"strong\">** 粗体 and <span class=\"emphasis\">_粗斜体_</span>**</span>.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">删除线波浪魔法： ~~ 消失啦~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>斜体魔法：<em>斜体</em>、_斜体_。</p>\n<p>粗体魔法： <strong>粗体 </strong> or <strong> 粗体</strong>.</p>\n<p>曦煦阁的秘密组合： <strong>粗体 and <em>粗斜体</em></strong>.</p>\n<p>删除线波浪魔法： <del>消失啦</del></p>\n<h2 id=\"列表\"><a href=\"# 列表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"列表~\"></a>列表~</h2><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">1.</span> 这是一个有序列表</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">2.</span> 第一项</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">  *</span> 这是一个带点的无序列表</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">1.</span> （其实数字不重要，只要是数字就行）</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">  1.</span> 有序子列表（记得加两个空格）</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">4.</span> 第二项</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">   （一般用三个空格来对齐）</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">*</span> 无序列表可以用<span class=\"emphasis\">* 号</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"emphasis\">- 或 - 号</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"emphasis\">+ 或 ＋ 号</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"emphasis\">- （特别适合段落连贯）</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<ol>\n<li>这是一个有序列表</li>\n<li>第一项</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>这是一个带点的无序列表</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li><p>（其实数字不重要，只要是数字就行）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>有序子列表（记得加两个空格）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>第二项</p>\n<p>（一般用三个空格来对齐）</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>无序列表可以用 * 号</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>或 - 号</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>或 ＋ 号</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>（特别适合段落连贯）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"HTML 类\"><a href=\"#HTML 类\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"HTML 类~\"></a>HTML 类~</h2><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span>想重启电脑，就按 <span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">kbd</span>&gt;</span></span>ctrl<span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">kbd</span>&gt;</span></span>+<span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">kbd</span>&gt;</span></span>alt<span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">kbd</span>&gt;</span></span>+<span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">kbd</span>&gt;</span></span>del<span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">kbd</span>&gt;</span></span>！<span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>想重启电脑，就按 <kbd>ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>alt</kbd>+<kbd>del</kbd>！</p>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"链接\"><a href=\"# 链接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"链接~\"></a>链接~</h2><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[<span class=\"string\">内联链接 </span>](<span class=\"link\">//www.google.com</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[<span class=\"string\"> 带有标题的内联链接 </span>](<span class=\"link\">//www.google.com &quot;Google!&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[<span class=\"string\"> 引用存储库</span>](<span class=\"link\">../blob/master/LICENSE</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><a href=\"//www.google.com\">内联链接</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"//www.google.com\" title=\"Google!\">带有标题的内联链接</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"../blob/master/LICENSE\">引用存储库</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"关于图像\"><a href=\"# 关于图像\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"关于图像~\"></a>关于图像~</h2><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">鼠标悬停以查看标题文本：</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">![<span class=\"string\">这里写文本</span>](<span class=\"link\">/gallery/A1.png &quot;Logo 标题 1&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>鼠标悬停以查看标题文本：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/gallery/A1.png\" alt=\"这里写文本\" title=\"Logo 标题 1\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"高亮显示文本\"><a href=\"# 高亮显示文本\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"高亮显示文本~\"></a>高亮显示文本~</h2><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">高亮 <span class=\"code\">` 代码 `</span> 需要加上 <span class=\"code\">` 反引号 `</span> ！</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>高亮 <code>代码 </code> 需要加上 <code> 反引号</code> ！</p>\n<h2 id=\"表格\"><a href=\"# 表格\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"表格~\"></a>表格~</h2><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">|   | ABC     | DEF   |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| - | ------- | ----- |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| 1 | <span class=\"code\">`1abcd`</span> | aabcd |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| 2 | <span class=\"code\">`2abcd`</span> | babcd |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| 3 | <span class=\"code\">`3abcd`</span> | cabcd |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th>ABC</th>\n<th>DEF</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td><code>1abcd</code></td>\n<td>aabcd</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td><code>2abcd</code></td>\n<td>babcd</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td><code>3abcd</code></td>\n<td>cabcd</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"符号\"><a href=\"# 符号\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"&gt; 符号~\"></a>&gt; 符号~</h2><blockquote>\n<p>用于模拟回复文本。<br>（计划的一部分）</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Quote break.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这是一行很长的行，当它换行时仍然会被正确引用。ヾ (✿ﾟ▽ﾟ) ノ让我们继续写，让他真正的长~。对了，你还可以放入一个 <strong> 粗体魔法 </strong> 到这行文本内！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"分隔标\"><a href=\"# 分隔标\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"分隔标~\"></a>分隔标~</h2><p>Three or more…</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">---</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">连续的 -</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"strong\">***</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"strong\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"strong\">连续的 *</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"strong\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"strong\">___</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"strong\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"strong\">连续的<span class=\"emphasis\">_</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<p>连续的 -</p>\n<hr>\n<p>连续的 *</p>\n<hr>\n<p>连续的_</p>\n<h2 id=\"进阶技巧\"><a href=\"# 进阶技巧\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"进阶技巧~\"></a>进阶技巧~</h2><hr>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">table</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"code\">    &lt;tr&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"code\">        &lt;td&gt;awa&lt;/td&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"code\">    &lt;/tr&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"code\">&lt;/table&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<table>\n    <tr>\n        <td>awa</td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2 id=\"我的 BiliBili\"><a href=\"# 我的 BiliBili\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"我的 BiliBili~\"></a>我的 BiliBili~</h2><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">a</span> <span class=\"attr\">href</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;//space.bilibili.com/321210964</span></span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"><span class=\"tag\"><span class=\"language-xml\">&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">target</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;_blank&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">img</span> <span class=\"attr\">src</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;https://ts2.cn.mm.bing.net/th?id=ODLS.e42d2c4d-ad65-4c7a-b0fd-817a1c3bed01&amp;w=32&amp;h=32&amp;qlt=90&amp;pcl=fffffa&amp;o=6&amp;pid=1.2&quot;</span></span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"><span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"attr\">alt</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;IMAGE ALT TEXT HERE&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">width</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;240&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">height</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;180&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">border</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;10&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">a</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><a href=\"//space.bilibili.com/321210964\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ts2.cn.mm.bing.net/th?id=ODLS.e42d2c4d-ad65-4c7a-b0fd-817a1c3bed01&w=32&h=32&qlt=90&pcl=fffffa&o=6&pid=1.2\"\nalt=\"IMAGE ALT TEXT HERE\" width=\"240\" height=\"180\" border=\"10\" /></a></p>\n","url":"/posts/26104/","min2read":3,"word4post":726,"prev_post":null,"next_post":{"title":"第一篇个人博客介绍","url":"/posts/45029/"},"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"开头\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">开头~</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"H1\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">H1</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"H2\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">H2</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"H3\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.1.1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">H3</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"H4\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.1.1.1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">H4</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"H5\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.1.1.1.1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">H5</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-6\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"H6\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.1.1.1.1.1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">H6</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"Alt-H1\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">Alt-H1</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"Alt-H2\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">Alt-H2</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"强调字体\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.2.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">强调字体~</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"列表\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.3.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">列表~</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"HTML 类\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.4.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">HTML 类~</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"链接\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.5.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">链接~</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"关于图像\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.6.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">关于图像~</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"高亮显示文本\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.7.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">高亮显示文本~</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"表格\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.8.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">表格~</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"符号\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.9.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">&gt; 符号~</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"分隔标\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.10.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">分隔标~</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"进阶技巧\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.11.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">进阶技巧~</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"我的 BiliBili\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.12.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">我的 BiliBili~</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","categories":[{"name":"网站开发","path":"api/categories/网站开发.json","url":"/categories/网站开发/"}],"tags":[{"name":"MD语法","path":"api/tags/MD语法.json","url":"/tags/MD语法/"}]}